 the government should reconsider this bill government cannot increase the cess from rs 25 to 200 at one go it is eight  times  increase  this  amount  will  be  extorted  from  public  pockets  general public is suffering from pricerise already and country is facing a drought situation this  cess  will  worsen  the  situation  further  the  sugar  industry  is  facing  crisis  at present under frp payments have to be  made to farmers within 14 days but it was  not  done  and  no  action  was  taken  against  erring  directors  government  may help sugar industry with sugar development fund but not with the funds collected from farmers this bill will increase more burden on farmers government should adopt other methods to collect funds like using bioproducts to help this industry  